Maintainer: Shrikrishna Bhat K<skbhat.in@gmail.com>
Description: Offers tools for silhouette-based diagnostics in clustering, including standard clustering and n-way tensor clustering (e.g., biclustering, triclustering). Provides functions for computing silhouette widths, extended silhouette widths for multi-way clustering, and visualization tools to evaluate cluster quality and cohesion.
